sequenceDiagram
actor User as Członek/Muzyk
actor Admin as Moderator

participant Browser
participant View as SongView / ModerationView
participant Edit as EditProposal
participant Moderation as ModerationService
participant DB as Database
participant Song as Piosenka

%% =========================
%% EDIT PHASE (UC-15)
%% =========================

User->>Browser: Edit song
Browser->>View: submit edit

View->>Edit: create proposal (proposed_text, changes)
Edit->>Edit: store status = pending
Edit-->>View: proposal saved

View-->>Browser: confirmation
Browser-->>User: edit submitted for review

%% =========================
%% MODERATION PHASE (UC-16)
%% =========================

Admin->>Browser: Open moderation panel
Browser->>View: GET pending proposals

View->>Moderation: fetch pending EditProposals
Moderation-->>View: list of proposals

Admin->>Browser: Approve / Reject proposal
Browser->>View: moderation action

View->>Moderation: approve(proposal) / reject(proposal)

alt Approved
    Moderation->>Song: apply changes from proposal
    Moderation->>Edit: update status = approved
    Moderation->>DB: persist updated Piosenka
    DB-->>Moderation: success
else Rejected
    Moderation->>Edit: update status = rejected
end

Moderation-->>View: result
View-->>Browser: moderation confirmation
Browser-->>Admin: status updated